net.objectzoo.ebc.builder

Class SendsResultConnector<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.objectzoo.ebc.builder.SendsResultConnector<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the result of the last step in the flow

    public class SendsResultConnector<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Instances of this class allow the DSL like definition of EBC flows by attaching the next EBC to a flow that ended with a SendsResult or Event.
    Author:
    tilmann
